{
  "video_id": "3bj-ba3P_cU",
  "title": "Why open a school? To close a prison | Nadia Lopez",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12666.0,
      "end_time": 17246.0,
      "text": "When I opened Mott Hall Bridges Academy in 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18370.0,
      "end_time": 19674.0,
      "text": "my goal was simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20555.0,
      "end_time": 23563.0,
      "text": "open a school to close a prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24525.0,
      "end_time": 27509.0,
      "text": "Now to some, this was an audacious goal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27534.0,
      "end_time": 31160.0,
      "text": "because our school is located in the Brownsville section of Brooklyn --"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31773.0,
      "end_time": 34973.0,
      "text": "one of the most underserved and violent neighborhoods"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34997.0,
      "end_time": 37630.0,
      "text": "in all of New York City."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38121.0,
      "end_time": 41673.0,
      "text": "Like many urban schools with high poverty rates,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42427.0,
      "end_time": 44507.0,
      "text": "we face numerous challenges,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45173.0,
      "end_time": 47599.0,
      "text": "like finding teachers who can empathize"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47623.0,
      "end_time": 51220.0,
      "text": "with the complexities of a disadvantaged community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52540.0,
      "end_time": 54651.0,
      "text": "lack of funding for technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54675.0,
      "end_time": 56614.0,
      "text": "low parental involvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57433.0,
      "end_time": 63357.0,
      "text": "and neighborhood gangs that recruit children as early as fourth grade."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 64885.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66292.0,
      "text": "So here I was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67416.0,
      "end_time": 73142.0,
      "text": "the founding principal of a middle school that was a district public school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 73728.0,
      "end_time": 76854.0,
      "text": "and I only had 45 kids to start."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 78240.0,
      "end_time": 80540.0,
      "text": "Thirty percent of them had special needs."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 81797.0,
      "end_time": 84838.0,
      "text": "Eighty-six percent of them were below grade level"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 84862.0,
      "end_time": 86884.0,
      "text": "in English and in math."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 87701.0,
      "end_time": 91970.0,
      "text": "And 100 percent were living below the poverty level."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 93258.0,
      "end_time": 96567.0,
      "text": "If our children are not in our classrooms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 96591.0,
      "end_time": 97937.0,
      "text": "how will they learn?"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 98731.0,
      "end_time": 100505.0,
      "text": "And if they&#39;re not learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 100529.0,
      "end_time": 102231.0,
      "text": "where would they end up?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103402.0,
      "end_time": 108372.0,
      "text": "It was evident when I would ask my 13-year-old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 108396.0,
      "end_time": 109657.0,
      "text": "\"Young man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 109681.0,
      "end_time": 113180.0,
      "text": "where do you see yourself in five years?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 113663.0,
      "end_time": 115322.0,
      "text": "And his response:"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 115691.0,
      "end_time": 117912.0,
      "text": "\"I don&#39;t know if I&#39;m gonna live that long.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 118971.0,
      "end_time": 121847.0,
      "text": "Or to have a young woman say to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 123252.0,
      "end_time": 128232.0,
      "text": "that she had a lifelong goal of working in a fast-food restaurant."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 128800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130969.00000000001,
      "text": "To me, this was unacceptable."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 131862.0,
      "end_time": 135990.0,
      "text": "It was also evident that they had no idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 135123.0,
      "end_time": 137268.0,
      "text": "that there was a landscape of opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 137292.0,
      "end_time": 140400.0,
      "text": "that existed beyond their neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 141550.0,
      "end_time": 145799.0,
      "text": "We call our students \"scholars,\" because they&#39;re lifelong learners."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 146597.0,
      "end_time": 148377.0,
      "text": "And the skills that they learn today"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 148401.0,
      "end_time": 151722.0,
      "text": "will prepare them for college and career readiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 152931.0,
      "end_time": 157720.0,
      "text": "I chose the royal colors of purple and black,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 157786.0,
      "end_time": 162560.0,
      "text": "because I want them to be reminded that they are descendants of greatness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 162584.0,
      "end_time": 164409.0,
      "text": "and that through education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 164433.0,
      "end_time": 166480.0,
      "text": "they are future engineers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 166504.0,
      "end_time": 167666.0,
      "text": "scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 167690.0,
      "end_time": 169530.0,
      "text": "entrepreneurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 169770.0,
      "end_time": 173389.0,
      "text": "and even leaders who can and will take over this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 174544.0,
      "end_time": 175822.0,
      "text": "To date,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 175846.0,
      "end_time": 179348.0,
      "text": "we have had three graduating classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 179959.0,
      "end_time": 181345.0,
      "text": "at a 98 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 181369.0,
      "end_time": 185484.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 190341.0,
      "end_time": 193183.0,
      "text": "At a 98-percent graduation rate."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 194120.0,
      "end_time": 196953.0,
      "text": "This is nearly 200 children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 196977.0,
      "end_time": 200233.0,
      "text": "who are now going to some of the most competitive high schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 200257.0,
      "end_time": 201731.0,
      "text": "in New York City."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 201755.0,
      "end_time": 207319.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 209675.0,
      "end_time": 212186.0,
      "text": "It was a cold day in January"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 212872.0,
      "end_time": 216566.0,
      "text": "when my scholar, Vidal Chastanet, met Brandon Stanton,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 217462.0,
      "end_time": 221255.0,
      "text": "the founder of the popular blog \"Humans of New York.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 222102.0,
      "end_time": 225995.0,
      "text": "Brandon shared the story of a young man from Brownsville"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 226190.0,
      "end_time": 228739.0,
      "text": "who had witnessed violence firsthand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 229977.0,
      "end_time": 233502.0,
      "text": "by witnessing a man being thrown off of a roof."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 234264.0,
      "end_time": 237703.0,
      "text": "Yet he can still be influenced by a principal"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 237727.0,
      "end_time": 241204.0,
      "text": "who had opened up a school that believes in all children."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 242490.0,
      "end_time": 248950.0,
      "text": "Vidal embodies the story of so many of our underprivileged children"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 248119.0,
      "end_time": 250230.0,
      "text": "who are struggling to survive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 250859.0,
      "end_time": 254650.0,
      "text": "which is why we must make education a priority."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 255992.0,
      "end_time": 259204.0,
      "text": "Brandon&#39;s post created a global sensation"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 259228.0,
      "end_time": 261607.0,
      "text": "that touched the lives of millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 262855.0,
      "end_time": 266810.0,
      "text": "This resulted in 1.4 million dollars being raised"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 267390.0,
      "end_time": 273311.0,
      "text": "for our scholars to attend field trips to colleges and universities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 274100.0,
      "end_time": 276279.0,
      "text": "Summer STEAM programs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 276303.0,
      "end_time": 278594.0,
      "text": "as well as college scholarships."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 279792.0,
      "end_time": 280969.0,
      "text": "You need to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 280993.0,
      "end_time": 286462.0,
      "text": "that when 200 young people from Brownsville visited Harvard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 287308.0,
      "end_time": 289137.0,
      "text": "they now understood"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 289161.0,
      "end_time": 293431.0,
      "text": "that a college of their choice was a real possibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 294457.0,
      "end_time": 297895.0,
      "text": "And the impossibilities that had been imposed upon them"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 298431.0,
      "end_time": 300561.0,
      "text": "by a disadvantaged community"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 300585.0,
      "end_time": 304121.0,
      "text": "were replaced by hope and purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 305498.0,
      "end_time": 310484.0,
      "text": "The revolution in education is happening in our schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 311349.0,
      "end_time": 314703.0,
      "text": "with adults who provide love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 314727.0,
      "end_time": 315902.0,
      "text": "structure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 315927.0,
      "end_time": 317890.0,
      "text": "support"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 317113.0,
      "end_time": 318363.0,
      "text": "and knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 318963.0,
      "end_time": 321782.0,
      "text": "These are the things that inspire children."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 322806.0,
      "end_time": 325109.0,
      "text": "But it is not an easy task."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 325815.0,
      "end_time": 327854.0,
      "text": "And there are high demands"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 328709.0,
      "end_time": 331953.0,
      "text": "within an education system that is not perfect."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 332893.0,
      "end_time": 335849.0,
      "text": "But I have a dynamic group of educators"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 336756.0,
      "end_time": 341250.0,
      "text": "who collaborate as a team to determine what is the best curriculum."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 341553.0,
      "end_time": 344423.0,
      "text": "They take time beyond their school day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 344447.0,
      "end_time": 345744.0,
      "text": "and come in on weekends"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 345768.0,
      "end_time": 350220.0,
      "text": "and even use their own money to often provide resources"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 350921.0,
      "end_time": 352623.0,
      "text": "when we do not have it."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 353804.0,
      "end_time": 355652.0,
      "text": "And as the principal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 355676.0,
      "end_time": 358562.0,
      "text": "I have to inspect what I expect."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 359308.0,
      "end_time": 361157.0,
      "text": "So I show up in classes"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 361836.0,
      "end_time": 364922.0,
      "text": "and I conduct observations to give feedback,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 364946.0,
      "end_time": 368361.0,
      "text": "because I want my teachers to be just as successful"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 368385.0,
      "end_time": 370700.0,
      "text": "as the name Mott Hall Bridges Academy."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 371930.0,
      "end_time": 375622.0,
      "text": "And I give them access to me every single day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 375646.0,
      "end_time": 378510.0,
      "text": "which is why they all have my personal cell number,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 378534.0,
      "end_time": 381592.0,
      "text": "including my scholars and those who graduated --"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 381616.0,
      "end_time": 384574.0,
      "text": "which is probably why I get phone calls and text messages"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 384598.0,
      "end_time": 386362.0,
      "text": "at three o&#39;clock in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 386386.0,
      "end_time": 387571.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 388174.0,
      "end_time": 390770.0,
      "text": "But we are all connected to succeed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 390794.0,
      "end_time": 392702.0,
      "text": "and good leaders do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 394282.0,
      "end_time": 397546.0,
      "text": "Tomorrow&#39;s future is sitting in our classrooms."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 398304.0,
      "end_time": 400407.0,
      "text": "And they are our responsibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 401526.0,
      "end_time": 403503.0,
      "text": "That means everyone in here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 403527.0,
      "end_time": 405657.0,
      "text": "and those who are watching the screen."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 406649.0,
      "end_time": 409190.0,
      "text": "We must believe in their brilliance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 410234.0,
      "end_time": 412842.0,
      "text": "and remind them by teaching them"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 412867.0,
      "end_time": 417361.0,
      "text": "that there indeed is power in education."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 418470.0,
      "end_time": 419227.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 419251.0,
      "end_time": 429378.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}